r will it damage other devices, nor will the prongs get bent, and it can easily slip into most bags. Nice.\n\nYou deserve a faster-charging wall plug that minimizes cable clutter and doesnâ€™t take up much space itself. Go ahead and grab yourself the 65W Ugreen Nexode on Amazon for just $26 (was $43).\n\nSave 40% on this 4-device GaN charger wall plug"}
